Revision history for CSS-Font-Resources

{{$NEXT}}

0.0.5  2021-09-25T08:26:47+12:00
    - Bypass fontconfig depedent tests by default. Setting $TEST_FONT_CONFIG
      reenables these tests. This is sufficient for tests to pass on Windows.

0.0.4  2021-09-16T16:15:04+12:00
    - Add CSS::URI; factored out of CSS::Font::Resources::Source::URI

0.0.3  2021-09-11T11:59:51+12:00
    - Fixed font format mapping of `.pfb` files
    - Fixed fallback font pattern

0.0.2  2021-09-08T08:50:26+12:00
    - Add Str method. Returns a serialized URL or local path; suitable
      as a fetch-cache key.

0.0.1  2021-09-07T16:47:09+12:00
    - Initial version
